Di '''suol''' ina nof [[rilijan]], filasafikal ah mitolajikal chradishan, a di inkaaporal ah imaatal esn a libm biin.<ref>"soul."Encyclopædia Britannica. 2010. Encyclopædia Britannica 2006 CD. 13 July 2010.</ref> Askaadn tu [[Iebriamik rilijan]], onggl yuuman biin ab imaatal suol. Fi egzampl, di [[Ruoman Kiaklik Choch|Kiaklik]] tioluojan [[Tamas Akwainas]] achribiut "suol" (''[[:en:wikt:anima|anima]]'') tu aal [[aaganizim]] bot aagiu se onggl yuuman suol imaatal.<ref>Peter Eardley and Carl Still, ''Aquinas: A Guide for the Perplexed'' (London: Continuum, 2010), pp. 34–35</ref> Ada rilijan (muos nuotebl [[Induizim]] ah [[Jainizim]]) tiich se aal bailajikal aaganizim ab suol, wails som tiich se iibm nan-bailajikal entiti (laka riva ah mountn) pozes suol. Dis lata biliif nuo az [[animizim]].<ref>[http://wayback.archive.org/web/20080709052029/http://www.bartleby.com/65/so/soul.html "Soul"], ''The Columbia Encyclopedia'', Sixth Edition. 2001–07. Richriiv 12 November 2008.</ref>

Griik filasafa laka [[Sakratiiz]], [[Plieto]] ah [[Aristakl]] eh-andastan se di ''[[:en:wikt:ψυχή#Ancient Greek|psyche]]'' (ψυχή) mos ab lajikal fakolti, ah di exasaiz a it ena di muos divain a yuuman akshan. A ih difens chrayal, Sakratiiz iibm somaraiz ih tiichin az notn muo dah egzautieshan fi ih felo Atiinian fi exel ina mataz a di saiki sens aal badili gudz dipendant pah soch exilens (''[[Apalaji (Plieto)|Di Apalaji]]'' 30a–b).

''[[Anima mundi]]'' a di kansep a "wol suol" we kanekop aal libm aaganizim pah di planit.

